					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13111446#post-4534579</guid>
				<title>No relationship to the moderator Corvus...</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13111446/scp-5560#post-4534579</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2020 13:34:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Jacob Conwell</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1372582</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Alright, Series 6 is live and you just know I needed to get in at least one more of those XX60 spots before we move on to Series 7. It has been a while since I have written anything for Anderson Robotics or Those Twisted Pines, so this is a bit of a return to basics for me, with a largely character driven SCP. Additionally, I felt it was time to start exploring other asspects of the canon away from Vincent Anderson, Edgar Holman, and the Merlo family, so they are distinctly absent here.</p> <p>Special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583501661" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" >A Random Day</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583501661" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" >DrBleep</a></span> for holding the original drafts of this over the coals. Wouldn't be nearly as poignant without your input.</p> <p>Additional thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3352053&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583501661" alt="Cerastes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3352053)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" >Cerastes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4037075&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583501661" alt="Elogee FishTruck" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4037075)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/elogee-fishtruck" >Elogee FishTruck</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tawny0" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2244665&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583501661" alt="tawny0" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2244665)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tawny0" >tawny0</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4463776&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583501661" alt="N_Aepic_Fael" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4463776)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/n-aepic-fael" >N_Aepic_Fael</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583501661" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span> for critique.</p> <p>Finally, shoutout to my friend <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583501661" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span> for supplying the image, and allowing its use here/release under CC 3.0 by SA.</p> <p>Enjoy the article.</p> <p><em>JC</em></p> 
